title: Dream Day Wedding - Viva Las Vegas - New HOG - Wendy99
description:
Dream Day Wedding Viva Las Vegas - 130 MB


Plan a Dream Day Wedding in the exciting city of Las Vegas. Juggle important tasks while 
discovering the perfect items to deliver an elegant and flawless wedding. Complete over 60 
wedding challenges in vibrant Vegas locations.
Maintain your poise under pressure by overcoming obstacles and managing the demands and of high 
rolling couple. Purchase extravagant decorations, design custom accessories & choose an 
incredible honeymoon destination. With more mini games, puzzles, and wedding crisis levels than 
ever before - you'll hit the jackpot of fun!
